# Local state files contain plaintext credentials. The wild-west
# narrative is the point of this tier — but committing tfstate makes
# the same blast-radius worse. Keep it local-only until the squad sets
# up a real backend (see main.tf for the example backend "s3" block).
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfstate.backup
crash.log
crash.*.log
.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Variable files that may carry sensitive values
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
!example.tfvars
